Me-Bai was sold to provide rides for tourists in Thailand when she was three-and-a-half years old . 
  She didn't see her mother Mae Yui for three years . 
  After a 62-mile (100km) trek through the Thai jungle, the small elephant can be seen nuzzling her mother . 
  The pair were reunited in the Elephant Nature Park sanctuary in the north of the country . 
  The small elephant was recently rescued and brought to the sanctuary . 
 